{"tid":609791,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《月刊Friends》創刊號發布","createTime":"2018-03-29T10:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T10:27:29.000Z","uid":179081,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c62386c5e6bb962b7f6fa1a3ddece7b4a6eb3f","tid":609791,"uid":179081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T10:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/hoogPSp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FhoogPSp.jpg&h=2476146b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n動物朋友是一部寓教於樂的大眾作品。<br />\n蘊含著友誼、包容、成長與反璞歸真的內在價值。<br />\n在獨特的世界觀中，<br />\n展現了多采多姿的擬人化角色的魅力。<br />\n<br />\n為了發掘傳達更多樣的角色魅力，<br />\n我們決定因應時節推出不同主題。<br />\n<br />\n因此，隨著農曆狗年的到來，<br />\n《月刊Friends》選擇了「犬」作為主題，<br />\n準備了犬科相關的圖文與漫畫，<br />\n希望能為您帶來一段美好的時光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/XtKlsZ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FXtKlsZ8.jpg&h=16c9f9b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了有較佳的瀏覽體驗，<br />\n請您前往發布站閱讀：<br />\n<a href=\"https://japari.press/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjapari.press%2F&d=oizoEBJqYhngY9Rq5Z2et4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=512f5c3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://japari.press/</a>"}]}